contentrichtext.text: '''Admiral Nakhimov''' may refer to: * Russian Admiral [[Pavel Nakhimov]] * [[Admiral Nakhimov (film)|''Admiral Nakhimov'' (film)]], a 1947 Soviet film directed by Vsevolod Pudovkin * Ships named after the admiral: ** ''[[Admiral Nakhimov (ship)]]'' ** [[Russian armoured cruiser Admiral Nakhimov|Russian armoured cruiser ''Admiral Nakhimov'']], Russian armoured cruiser ** Former name of ''[[Chervona Ukraina]]'' light cruiser ** ''Admiral Nakhimov'', a [[Sverdlov class cruiser]] ** ''Admiral Nakhimov'', a [[Kresta II class cruiser]] ** ''Admiral Nakhimov'', formerly Kalinin a [[Kirov class battlecruiser]] {{disambig}}
